From: Richard Hatchett <rhatchet@nyhs.med.cornell.edu>
I can't help observing that, in the spirit of robbing Peter to pay Paul,
the recent successes in mammalian cloning, the ethical issues
notwithstanding, must provide solace to those concerned about declining
human sperm counts.
